Step 1: Jumbotron 

	Create a div with "jumbotron text-center" (<div class="jumbotron text-center"></div>)

	Add a heading and a paragraph (h1 tag and p tag)

Step 2: Form 

	Create a form with the following fields:

	Name (type text)

	Email (type email)

	How do you rate boostrap? (Select box)

	What are your thoughts on Bootstrap? (Text box)

	Differences from a regular form: 

	Wrap label + input with a form group (<div class="form-group">label input</div>)

	<input class="form-control"></input>

	Put everything in a container (<div class="container"></div>)

Step 3: Carousel 
	
	Make the Carousel (<div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="myCarousel"></div>)

	Add the indicators:
 
	<ol class="carousel-indicators">
		<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
		<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
		...
	</ol>

	Add the items:

      	<div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
		<div class="item active">
		  <img src="GalaxyCluster.jpg" alt="Space">
		</div>

		<div class="item">
		  <img src="InteractingGalaxies.jpg" alt="Space">
		</div>
		...
	</div>

	Add the controls:

	<a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
		<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
	</a>
      	<a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
		<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      	</a>

	Add the style:

	<style>
	.carousel-inner > .item > img {
	        width: 70%;
     		margin: auto;
      		height: 500px;
  	}
  	</style>

Step 4: Grid

	Put the grid and carousel in a row:

	<div class="row">form carousel</div>
	
	Make the form and carousel six columns wide on medium:

	<div class="col-md-6">form</div> <div class="col-md-6">carousel</div>

Step 5: Add the navbar
	
	Create the nav OUTSIDE the container: 

	<nav class="navbar navbar-default"></nav>

	Add a container fluid container inside the nav:
	    
	<div class="container-fluid"></div>

	Add a navbar header:

	<div class="navbar-header">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Bootstrap Demo</a>
      	</div>

	Add list elements: 

      	<ul class="nav navbar-nav">
		<li class="active"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
		<li><a href="#">Page 1</a></li>
		<li><a href="#">Page 2</a></li>
		<li><a href="#">Page 3</a></li>
      	</ul>

	Add a margin of 0 to the jumbotron:

	.jumbotron {
        	margin: 0;
    	}
	
